                "description": {
                    "value": "<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p>The target can't reduce its sickened condition while affected by rompo chills;</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"disease\" data-pf2-label=\"Rompo Chills DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"19\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span>;</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\">\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 1 day;</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> Clumsy 1 and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 2} (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 4</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} (1 day);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 5</strong> dead</p>\n</div>"
